@NODE MAIN
@TITLE "KidLock · Index"


    @{b}KidLock 1.1 @{ub}

    KidLock protects the computer from accidental key strokes and mouse moves
    or clicks by kids, cats, turtles or other fellow lodgers who don't know
    how to use a computer properly.

