@NODE Future
@TITLE "KidLock · Future"


    @{b}Future@{ub}


    o Display pictures and play sounds on each keystroke to make typing more
      entertaining for kids.
      Currently, a single picture is ready: a duck. Will be for later.

    o Catch the 3-finger-salute (Ctrl + Left Command + Right Command)
      Still on the TODO but might be impossible to catch in a system-friendly
      way. See @{"FAQ" link FAQ}.

    o Add settings in the preferences pane of the screenbar module.


